Thanks Jermyn for the great experience!

text:

There‚Äôs a power rack, booty builder, functional area, and a nice mix of cardio machines (facing the HV food street ‚Äî kind of cool view). It feels cozy and not too crowded if you go at the right time.

Staff are friendly, place is clean, and there‚Äôs even spin classes weekly. Just don‚Äôt expect big gym vibes ‚Äî no deadlift platform or assisted pull-up machine here. But if you like chill, simple workouts in a convenient location, this spot does the job!

I would say if you are looking to move towards your fitness goals and have the capital to do so, Jermyn is someone you can approach at this AF outlet.

author: soon oh
text:

author: D T
text:
Sharing my experience with my trainer Firdaus Aziz at at Anytime Fitness Holland Village.

I‚Äôve really appreciated my training sessions over the past 8 months with Firdaus. As a middle-aged guy who hadn‚Äôt exercised for over a decade, I was completely clueless when I first joined the gym. Thankfully, with Firdaus‚Äôs patience and friendly guidance, I gradually gained confidence and achieved both my weight loss and strength-building goals.

One aspect I truly value about Firdaus is his deep knowledge of his craft. He doesn‚Äôt just demonstrate the exercises, he takes the time to explain how and why each exercise works, in a way that‚Äôs easy for a layman like me to understand. This helped me understand how the workouts will really benefit me in the long run, beyond just going through the motions.

Firdaus also goes beyond the gym floor. His practical advice on lifestyle and nutrition encouraged me to break old habits and adopt a healthier way of living, step by step.

And to top it all off, his friendly and approachable personality makes even the most challenging sessions enjoyable - as he pushes me to go further, I always feel supported and not rushed.

If anyone in the neighbourhood is looking for a personal trainer, I highly recommend checking in with Firdaus.

author: Vivian Han
text:
Excellent Service at Anytime Fitness Holland Village!

I had a fantastic experience with the team at Anytime Fitness Holland Village! After facing a frustrating issue with my membership cancellation at the Jurong East branch, the staff at Holland Village went above and beyond to help me resolve the situation quickly and smoothly.

They were professional, understanding, and super efficient in assisting me with the cancellation process. Unlike the poor communication I experienced at the other branch, the Holland Village team provided clear instructions and ensured everything was handled properly without any last-minute surprises.

I truly appreciate their dedication to customer service and willingness to step in and fix a problem caused by another location. If you‚Äôre looking for a gym with friendly and reliable staff, I highly recommend Anytime Fitness Holland Village! Thank you so much for turning a bad situation into a positive experience!

Training & Nutrition has been really tailored to the specific goals that I was working on, and she's creative to switch up things along the weeks to spice things up so it won't be repetitive/boring/routine based. Much effort and dedication are put into the work she does, evidently seen through her actions.

Outlet review:
It's a cozy and nice outlet, crowd is quite okay. Has sufficient equipment enough to do all your exercises. Has a good range of light-Medium, semi advanced weight range. Would recommend if your level of exercising is between beginner/Intermediate/slightly advance.

author: Parry
text:
If you‚Äôre seeing this, take it as a sign to not sign up with holland AF. Scam company that lies to customers and will not honour promotion (yes even if you sign). So please, I implore you, think twice

The 5 star reviews below are probably for members whose contract have not lapsed yet.

But please refrain from signing up with holland AF.

Basically when I signed up, was promised 2 free months if I paid upfront for 1.5 years. Sounds like a great deal, I signed and paid, took picture of the contract and got WhatsApp confirmation from the staff. Months later I broke my arm as well, and got confirmation that my membership has been paused for 4 months.

Long story short these months that were promised to me were not logged into the system.

Whatsapped them but they did not even want to send me the original contract I signed with them. Suspicious right? Kept saying that I‚Äôm no longer in their gym and transferred elsewhere so they don‚Äôt have access to any of my info. Rlly?? I doubt that all history of members are erased just like that.

I hope that more investigation can be done on this matter and if not, I hope that this review can prevent someone else from falling for such cheap tricks.
